Description_lang: Cause a violent eruption beneath an enemy's feet, dealing $s1 Volcanic damage split between them and nearby enemies.$?s395153[Increases the duration of your active Ebon Might effects by ${$395153s1/1000} sec.][]

description_blz.en_US: Cause a violent eruption beneath an enemy's feet, dealing 15,495 Volcanic damage split between them and nearby enemies.
description_blz.es_MX: Causa una erupción violenta bajo tu enemigo que inflige 15,495 p. de daño volcánico que se divide entre el enemigo alcanzado y los enemigos cercanos.
description_blz.pt_BR: Causa uma erupção violenta sob os pés de um inimigo, causando 15.495 de dano Vulcânico dividido entre ele e inimigos próximos.
description_blz.de_DE: Löst eine heftige Eruption unter den Füßen eines Gegners aus und verursacht 15.495 Vulkanschaden, der gleichmäßig zwischen ihm und Gegnern in der Nähe aufgeteilt wird.
description_blz.en_GB: Cause a violent eruption beneath an enemy's feet, dealing 15,495 Volcanic damage split between them and nearby enemies.
description_blz.es_ES: Provoca una violenta erupción bajo los pies de un enemigo que inflige 15495 p. de daño Volcánico a dividir entre los enemigos cercanos.
description_blz.fr_FR: Déclenche une violente éruption sous les pieds de l’ennemi, ce qui inflige 15495 points de dégâts volcaniques répartis entre lui et les ennemis proches.
description_blz.it_IT: Causa una violenta eruzione sotto i piedi del nemico, infliggendo 15.495 danni vulcanici suddivisi tra il bersaglio e i nemici vicini.
description_blz.ru_RU: Вызывает под ногами противника мощное извержение, наносящее 15495 ед. вулканического урона, распределяемого между целью и ближайшими к ней противниками.
description_blz.ko_KR: 적의 발밑에 격렬한 분출을 일으켜 대상과 주위의 적에게 15,495의 화산 피해를 나누어 입힙니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 在一個敵人腳下產生猛烈爆發，造成15,495點熔岩傷害，由目標和附近敵人平均分攤。
description_blz.zh_CN: 在一名敌人脚下引发剧烈喷发，造成15,495点熔火伤害，由目标和附近的所有敌人均摊。
